Package: mix2mgsem
Type: Package
Title: Two-Step Double-Mixture Multigroup Structural Equation Modeling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Hongwei",
      family = "Zhao",
      email = "hongwei.zhao@kuleuven.be",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements a two-step double-mixture multigroup structural
    equation modeling workflow. The first step clusters groups based on
    measurement-model parameters using mixture multigroup factor analysis.
    The second step clusters groups based on structural relations using
    group-specific factor covariance matrices from the first step as input.
